1. Overview
This is a simple Todo List application built with Angular that allows users to manage their tasks efficiently. Users can create, edit, delete, and filter todos based on priority, tags, and assigned users.
2. Features Implemented
Todo Management
    • Create new todos with title and description
    • Add tags and priority (High, Medium, Low)
    • Mention other users using @username
    • Edit existing todos
    • Delete todos
Todo Details
    • Click on a todo to view its details
    • Add notes via a modal when clicking the "Add Note" button
List View Features
    • Display all todos in a structured list
    • Filter todos by tags, priority, or users
    • Sort todos by creation date, priority, etc.

3. Technology Stack
    • Frontend: Angular, TypeScript, HTML, CSS
    • Backend: Node.js (Express)
    • Storage: Local Storage / API

4. Installation & Setup
bash
CopyEdit
# Clone the repository
git clone <repo_url>

# Navigate to the project folder
cd todo-list

# Install dependencies
npm install

# Run the application
ng serve

Visit http://localhost:4200/ to access the application.

